#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "how to configure SSL"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#, no-wrap
msgid "RHEL / Centos / etc"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    $ openssl req -new -newkey rsa:1024 -days 730 -nodes -x509 -keyout "
"glpi.mycompany.com.key -out glpi.mycompany.com.crt\n"
"    Generating a 1024 bit RSA private key\n"
"    ......++++++\n"
"    ...............++++++\n"
"    writing new private key to 'glpi.mycompany.com.key'\n"
"    -----\n"
"    You are about to be asked to enter information that will be "
"incorporated\n"
"    into your certificate request.\n"
"    What you are about to enter is what is called a Distinguished Name or a "
"DN.\n"
"    There are quite a few fields but you can leave some blank\n"
"    For some fields there will be a default value,\n"
"    If you enter '.', the field will be left blank.\n"
"    -----\n"
"    Country Name (2 letter code) [GB]:FR\n"
"    State or Province Name (full name) [Berkshire]:Ile de France\n"
"    Locality Name (eg, city) [Newbury]:Paris\n"
"    Organization Name (eg, company) [My Company Ltd]:\n"
"    Organizational Unit Name (eg, section) []:\n"
"    Common Name (eg, your name or your server's hostname) "
"[]:glpi.mycompany.com\n"
"    Email Address []:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This will generate a glpi.mycompany.com.key and a "
"glpi.mycompany.com.crt. Save them:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"     # cp glpi.mycompany.com.key /etc/pki/tls/private/\n"
"     # cp glpi.mycompany.com.crt /etc/pki/tls/certs/\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"CAUTION: assuming your URL to contact server is "
"http(s)://glpi.mycompany.com/. You (should) inform in file names and (have to) in "
"\"Common Name\" the name of your server."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Now you need to configure Apache so it will use these file:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"     # yum install mod_ssl\n"
"     # vi /etc/httpd/conf.d/ssl.conf\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "adjust SSLCertificateFile and SSLCertificateKeyFile"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "     # service httpd reload\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"glpi.mycompany.com.crt is the public certificat to use with your agent "
"(`--ca-cert-file=glpi.mycompany.com.crt`)."
msgstr ""
